18
The Legislative Evaluation and Development Committee shall review
18
19
financing for individual incentive packages including, but not
19
20
limited to, packages offering tax incentives, funds for economic
20
21
development, and, when the annual investment exceeds Twenty Million
21
22
Dollars ($20,000,000.00), excluding funding from existing incentives
